Coarsely chop the DOVE(R) PROMISES(R) Milk Chocolate and melt them either in a bowl on top of a double boiler or in the microwave for 1 to 1-1/2 minutes. Stir the chocolate until smooth. Add the sugar, butter, eggs and almond extract. Stir in the flour and baking powder. Add 1 cup of chopped SNICKERS(R) Brand Miniatures. Drop heaping tablespoons of batter on an ungreased cookie sheet. Bake in a preheated oven at 350 degrees for 10 to 12 minutes. Cool on the cookie sheet.